title: Jordan Peterson in SF on May 2 plus Meetup before Event
description:
Jordan Peterson is speaking at a private event hosted by the Independent Institute on May 2 2019 at 6:30. You can go if you join the Independent Institute and then purchase tickets. http://www.independent.org/events/detail.asp?id=180 

The Sacramento JBP Meetup group will have a meetup on site in the hotel from 4 to 6pm. Space is limited so if you're interested in coming sign up here after you purchase your ticket. https://www.meetup.com/Sacramento-Jordan-Peterson-Meetup/events/260911394/

Here is the Sacramento JBP Meetup page. https://www.meetup.com/Sacramento-Jordan-Peterson-Meetup

CS Lewis Society of California https://www.lewissociety.org/
Book club https://www.lewissociety.org/book-film-club/

I'll be leading the sessions on 12 Rules for Life on June 5 and 19.
